title.rendered: Seaside Family Medicine Presents 5 Years of Health & Wellness: Nurturing Well-being

content.rendered:
Seaside Family Medicine, a leading provider of health and wellness, is excited to invite the community to its upcoming event, 5 Years of Health & Wellness.

We believe in empowering individuals to take charge of their health and well-being through knowledge and personalized treatment options.”

— Amanda McAllister, DNP, PNP

SUMMERVILLE, SOUTH CAROLINA, USA, October 24, 2023 /EINPresswire.com/ — This unique event will provide valuable insights into individual needs and goals while celebrating our 5 year anniversary and amazing services!

Taking place on October 26th from 5:30 – 7:30 pm at 1708 Old Trolley Road Suite C Summerville, SC 29485. 5 Years of Health & Wellness promises an evening filled with knowledge-sharing, interactive discussions, and a chance to win amazing prizes. Attendees will have the opportunity to meet Seaside Family Medicine’s team of highly skilled health professionals and gain a deeper understanding of our services.

During the event, participants will learn about the latest advancements in Votiva, Medical Weight Loss, Evolve, and Morpheus. Seaside Family Medicine’s experts will share valuable insights, evidence-based practices, and practical tips to help attendees make informed decisions about their health and well-being.

As a special treat, light refreshments and champagne will be served, adding to the festive atmosphere of the event. Guests can enjoy refreshing beverages while engaging in meaningful conversations with the practitioners and fellow attendees.

In addition to the informative sessions and delightful refreshments, attendees will also have the opportunity to win fabulous prizes that include a free M8 Radiofrequency Microneedling Treatment and a free Evolve Body Toning Fat Burning Treatment. To double their chances of winning, guests are encouraged to bring a friend along.

“We are thrilled to host the 5 Years of Health & Wellness event and provide a platform to educate the community about our amazing prizes,” said Amanda McAllister at Seaside Family Medicine. “We believe in empowering individuals to take charge of their health and well-being through knowledge and personalized treatment options. 5 Years of Health & Wellness offers a unique opportunity to engage with our team of experts, ask questions, and discover the potential of our services.”

To reserve a spot at 5 Years of Health & Wellness, interested individuals are encouraged to register in advance by visiting https://seasidefamilymedicinepatients.com/5th-anniversary. Space is limited, so early registration is recommended to secure a spot at this highly anticipated event.

For media inquiries, please contact:

Amanda McAllister

DNP, PNP

(843) 471-2311

admin@seasidefamilymedicine.com

About Seaside Family Medicine:

At Seaside Family Medicine we care about health and well being and look forward to building life-long relationships with individuals and families. We want to provide patients with the best possible healthcare experience in a positive and relaxed environment so that one looks forward to their next visit with us. Our providers are highly skilled and experienced nurse practitioners trained in both adult and pediatric medicine.Seaside Family Medicine is a female-owned, mother-daughter team that cares deeply about quality care and their patients.

Amanda McAllister
Seaside Family Medicine
+1 843-471-2311
